#: luducat/ui/dialogs/setup_wizard.py:246
msgid ""
"Browse, organize, and explore — launching is handled by your platform's "
"native launcher."
msgstr ""
"Durchsuchen, organisieren und entdecken — das Starten übernimmt der "
"native Launcher deiner Plattform."

